description: We serve fresh French-Vietnamese Cuisine.  Some of our menu items include: several kinds of Pho, Spring rolls, Banh Mi Sandwiches, Jalapeno-Ginger Chicken, Crispy Crepes, Pho King Stir Fry, and rotating specials. As a food truck, we are always on the street. We also offer catering for a wide range of events from large to small.  For each catering event, we customize the menu to meet the needs of our customers.
name: The Great Pho King
